dashboard.description:
OKR 1: Entender onde há um maior gasto
Objective: Identificar e entender as principais categorias de despesas pessoais.
----------------------------------------------------------------
Key Results:

1. Rastrear todas as despesas diárias por 3 meses.
2. Categorizar todas as despesas em pelo menos 5 categorias principais.
3. Analisar o histórico de despesas para identificar as 3 maiores categorias de gasto.
4. Reduzir os gastos em pelo menos uma das três maiores categorias em 10% até o final do trimestre.
5. Criar um relatório mensal detalhado das despesas.

----------------------------------------------------------------
KPIs:

1. Percentual de despesas rastreadas mensalmente.
2. Número de categorias de despesas identificadas.
3. Percentual de redução nos gastos nas categorias principais.
4. Frequência de análise e relatório de despesas (mensalmente).
5. Valor total das despesas mensais em comparação com meses anteriores.

panels.description: Total de meses gerenciando os gastos

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  COUNT(DISTINCT DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%Y-%m')) AS number_of_months
FROM
  bk_tb_transactions;

panels.title: Total Meses

panels.description: Valor gasto por mê e comparativo com mês anterior

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  sum(A.value) as ammount,
  month(A.date) as month
FROM
  bk_tb_transactions A
  join bk_tb_categories B on A.category = B.id
where
  B.positive is false
  and B.internal is false
GROUP BY
  month(A.date)

panels.title: Gastos por mês

targets.rawSql:
SELECT A.date as data
     , A.description as descricao
     , B.name as categoria
     , CASE WHEN B.positive THEN A.value ELSE A.value * -1 END as valor
     , C.name as conta
  FROM bk_tb_transactions A
  JOIN bk_tb_categories B on A.category = B.id
  join bk_tb_accounts C on A.account = C.id
  ORDER BY A.date DESC
  LIMIT 50

SELECT
  SUM(A.value) AS TOTAL,
  B.name
FROM
  bk_tb_transactions A
  JOIN bk_tb_categories B ON A.category = B.id
WHERE
  B.positive IS FALSE
  AND B.internal IS FALSE
GROUP BY
  A.category
ORDER BY
  TOTAL DESC
LIMIT
  5

SELECT count(A.id) as transactions
     , month(A.date) as month
  FROM bk_tb_transactions A
--  WHERE A.date >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)
 GROUP BY month(A.date)

panels.description: Total de categorias registradas no mês

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  count(A.category) as categories,
  month(A.date) as month
FROM
  bk_tb_transactions A
  join bk_tb_categories B on A.category = B.id
where
  B.positive is false
  and B.internal is false
GROUP BY
  month(A.date)

panels.title: Categorias registradas

targets.rawSql:
WITH
  QuarterlyCategorySpend AS (
    SELECT
      A.category,
      CONCAT(YEAR(A.date), '-', MONTH(A.date)) AS month,
      SUM(A.value) AS total_spent,
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
        PARTITION BY
          YEAR(A.date),
          MONTH(A.date)
        ORDER BY
          SUM(A.value) DESC
      ) AS rank
    FROM
      bk_tb_transactions A
      join bk_tb_categories D on A.category = D.id
    where
      D.internal is false
      and D.positive is false
    GROUP BY
      A.category,
      YEAR(A.date),
      MONTH(A.date)
  )
SELECT
  B.month,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 1 THEN C.name
    END
  ) AS cat1,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 1 THEN B.total_spent
    END
  ) AS cat_value1,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 2 THEN C.name
    END
  ) AS cat2,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 2 THEN B.total_spent
    END
  ) AS cat_value2,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 3 THEN C.name
    END
  ) AS cat3,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 3 THEN B.total_spent
    END
  ) AS cat_value3
FROM
  QuarterlyCategorySpend B
  join bk_tb_categories C on B.category = C.id
WHERE
  B.rank <= 3
GROUP BY
  B.month
ORDER BY
  B.month;

panels.description: Apenas contas com saldo diferente de 0

targets.rawSql:
select a.name
     , a.ammount
  from bk_tb_accounts a
  where a.ammount != 0
  order by a.name asc

panels.description: Top 3 categorias por trimestre com comparativo de redução

targets.rawSql:
WITH
  QuarterlyCategorySpend AS (
    SELECT
      A.category,
      CONCAT('T', QUARTER(date), '-', YEAR(date)) AS quarter,
      SUM(value) AS total_spent,
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
        PARTITION BY
          YEAR(A.date),
          QUARTER(A.date)
        ORDER BY
          SUM(value) DESC
      ) AS rank
    FROM
      bk_tb_transactions A 
    join bk_tb_categories B on A.category = B.id
    where B.positive is false and B.internal is false
    GROUP BY
      A.category,
      YEAR(A.date),
      QUARTER(A.date)
  ),
  Top3Categories AS (
    SELECT
      quarter,
      category,
      total_spent,
      rank,
      LAG(total_spent) OVER (
        PARTITION BY
          category
        ORDER BY
          quarter
      ) AS prev_total_spent
    FROM
      QuarterlyCategorySpend
    WHERE
      rank <= 3
  )
SELECT
  A.quarter as trimestre,
  A.category,
  B.name as categoria,
  A.total_spent as 'Valor gasto' ,
  A.prev_total_spent as 'Valor ganto anterior',
  CASE
    WHEN A.prev_total_spent IS NOT NULL THEN (
      (A.prev_total_spent - A.total_spent) / A.prev_total_spent
    ) * 100
    ELSE NULL
  END AS 'Percentual de redução'
FROM
  Top3Categories A
  join bk_tb_categories B on A.category = B.id
ORDER BY
  A.quarter,
  A.rank;

WITH
  QuarterlyCategorySpend AS (
    SELECT
      A.category,
      CONCAT('T', QUARTER(A.date), '-', YEAR(A.date)) AS quarter,
      SUM(A.value) AS total_spent,
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
        PARTITION BY
          YEAR(A.date),

      ) AS rank
    FROM
      bk_tb_transactions A

      and D.positive is false
    GROUP BY
      A.category,

      QUARTER(A.date)
  )
SELECT
  B.quarter,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 1 THEN C.name
    END
  ) AS cat1,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 1 THEN B.total_spent
    END
  ) AS cat_value1,
  MAX(
    CASE
      WHEN B.rank = 2 THEN C.name
    END

      WHEN B.rank = 2 THEN B.total_spent
    END
